value.title: Applying Machine Learning to your Data with GCP
value.excerpt: Want to know how to query and process petabytes of data in seconds? Curious about data analysis that scales automatically as your data grows? Welcome to the Data Insights course! This accelerated online course teaches participants how to derive insights through data analysis and visualization using the Google Cloud Platform. The course features interactive scenarios and hands-on labs where participants explore, mine, load, visualize, and extract insights from diverse Google BigQuery datasets. The course covers data loading, querying, schema modeling, optimizing performance, query pricing,  and data visualization.

images.title: Applying Machine Learning to your Data with GCP

value.title: Architecting Production-ready ML Models Using Google Cloud ML Engine
value.excerpt: This course covers Cloud ML Engine, a powerful service that supports distributed training and evaluation for models built in TensorFlow, Scikit-learn and XGBoost.

images.title: Architecting Production-ready ML Models Using Google Cloud ML Engine

value.title: Designing and Implementing Solutions Using Google Cloud AutoML
value.excerpt: Google Cloud AI offers a wide range of machine learning services. AutoML features cutting-edge technology which uses your training data to find the best model for your use case. In this course, you'll learn to build a custom machine learning model.

images.title: Designing and Implementing Solutions Using Google Cloud AutoML

value.title: Designing and Implementing Solutions Using Google Machine Learning APIs
value.excerpt: Most organizations wish to harness the power of machine learning (ML) to improve their products, but they may not always have the expertise available in-house. This course shows you how to harness the power of ML for use cases using API calls.

images.title: Designing and Implementing Solutions Using Google Machine Learning APIs

value.title: Smart Analytics, Machine Learning, and AI on GCP
value.excerpt: Incorporating machine learning into data pipelines increases the ability of businesses to extract insights from their data. This course covers several ways machine learning can be included in data pipelines on Google Cloud Platform depending on the level of customization required. For little to no customization, this course covers AutoML. For more tailored machine learning capabilities, this course introduces AI Platform Notebooks and BigQuery Machine Learning. Also, this course covers how to productionalize machine learning solutions using Kubeflow. Learners will get hands-on experience building machine learning models on Google Cloud Platform using QwikLabs.

images.title: Smart Analytics, Machine Learning, and AI on GCP
